spec_data.Name: perl-Time-Interval
spec_data.Description:
This is a rather simple perl module for dealing with time intervals. Among
other things, this module can tell you the number of hours, minutes, and
seconds elapsed between two dates.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 15 Aug 2017 05:47:52 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Perl module that converts time intervals of days, hours, minutes, and seconds
